", 'start': 11.199, 'duration': 5.641}, {'text': 'Before making our salted caramels...', 'start': 16.84, 'duration': 2.21}, {'text': 'we always make sure we have our equipment
ready and all ingredients measured out...', 'start': 19.05, 'duration': 4.399}, {'text': 'here is a loaf pain, we are going to lightly oil it...', 'start': 23.449, 'duration': 3.361}, {'text': 'then we are going to cut a piece of parchment paper...', 'start': 26.81, 'duration': 3.07}, {'text': 'lightly oil that...', 'start': 29.88, 'duration': 1.609}, {'text': 'and then insert that inside the loaf pan...', 'start': 31.489, 'duration': 3.181}, {'text': 'which makes our lives a lot easier when we want to unmold the caramels when we are done.', 'start': 34.67, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'Next for the ingredients, we need to measure a half cup...', 'start': 41.92, 'duration': 4.33}, {'text': 'of heavy whipping cream.', 'start': 46.25, 'duration': 3.76}, {'text': 'Then grab one stick of butter which is also about a half cup...', 'start': 50.01, 'duration': 4.41}, {'text': 'and cut that into eight...', 'start': 54.42, 'duration': 1.95}, {'text': 'equally sized pieces.', 'start': 56.37, 'duration': 3.58}, {'text': 'Add that to a bowl...', 'start': 59.95, 'duration': 2.11}, {'text': 'then add the cream...', 'start': 62.06, 'duration': 2.69}, {'text': 'and place it into the microwave...', 'start': 64.75, 'duration': 4.4}, {'text': 'and cook for about a minute until the
butter has melted and the cream is hot...', 'start': 69.15, 'duration': 6.49}, {'text': 'set that aside...', 'start': 75.64, 'duration': 1.28}, {'text': 'and measure out a quarter cup of light corn syrup...', 'start': 76.92, 'duration': 3.37}, {'text': 'and one cup of granulated white sugar.', 'start': 80.29, 'duration': 5.56}, {'text': 'Now grab a small saucepan...', 'start': 85.85, 'duration': 3.59}, {'text': 'add three tablespoons of water to the saucepan...', 'start': 89.44, 'duration': 6.93}, {'text': 'then grab the corn syrup that you just measured out and add that to the saucepan.', 'start': 96.37, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'Next for the sugar...', 'start': 104.35, 'duration': 1.82}, {'text': 'add it, but try your best not to splatter the sugar up the sides of the pan.', 'start': 106.17, 'duration': 4.7}, {'text': 'Then just use a spoon or spatula...', 'start': 110.87, 'duration': 2.37}, {'text': 'to stir the sugar into the water and corn syrup. ', 'start': 113.24, 'duration': 4.25}, {'text': 'Heat to medium...', 'start': 117.49, 'duration': 1.11}, {'text': 'then bring to a boil.', 'start': 118.6, 'duration': 1.79}, {'text': "Now once it is at a boil we want to make sure there isn't...", 'start': 120.39, 'duration': 3.28}, {'text': 'any sugar crystals stuck to the side of the pan...', 'start': 123.67, 'duration': 2.38}, {'text': 'since this can cause something called crystallization which can make your caramels grainy...', 'start': 126.05, 'duration': 4.6}, {'text': 'and really ruin the texture.', 'start': 130.65, 'duration': 2.33}, {'text': 'To help with this, just cover with the lid for about one minute.', 'start': 132.98, 'duration': 4.019}, {'text': 'Remove the lid and attach a candy thermometer. ', 'start': 136.999, 'duration': 3.25}, {'text': 'You will want to cook the sugar until it reaches 320 degrees F.', 'start': 140.249, 'duration': 4.41}, {'text': 'At this temperature the sugar will take on a light amber color...', 'start': 146.159, 'duration': 4.78}, {'text': 'now we are ready to add the butter and cream mixture from before...', 'start': 150.939, 'duration': 3.92}, {'text': 'add it in small batches then use the candy thermometer to stir it into the sugar mixture. ', 'start': 154.859, 'duration': 5.05}, {'text': 'As you do this the caramel will bubble violently...', 'start': 161.519, 'duration': 4.271}, {'text': 'so you really want to do this slowly and
carefully so nothing bubbles over. ', 'start': 165.79, 'duration': 5.33}, {'text': 'Now place the candy thermometer...', 'start': 171.12, 'duration': 2.55}, {'text': 'back on the side of the pan...', 'start': 173.67, 'duration': 1.519}, {'text': 'and cook the caramel to 240 degrees F...', 'start': 175.189, 'duration': 4.211}, {'text': 'this will create a soft caramel.', 'start': 179.4, 'duration': 2.529}, {'text': 'If you want harder caramels...', 'start': 181.929, 'duration': 2.12}, {'text': 'cook to about 245 degrees F. ', 'start': 184.049, 'duration': 3.79}, {'text': 'Now pour the caramel into your prepared loaf pan...', 'start': 187.839, 'duration': 4.3}, {'text': 'and let it sit for about fifteen to twenty minutes. ', 'start': 192.139, 'duration': 5.38}, {'text': "While you wait it's best to clean your pot and candy thermometer...", 'start': 197.519, 'duration': 3.99}, {'text': 'fill the pot with water, place the candy thermometer into the water...', 'start': 201.509, 'duration': 4.27}, {'text': 'and bring the water to a boil...', 'start': 205.779, 'duration': 2.09}, {'text': 'this will melt away all of the caramel...', 'start': 207.869, 'duration': 2.75}, {'text': 'making cleanup really easy.', 'start': 210.619, 'duration': 4.89}, {'text': 'After about three and a half...', 'start': 215.509, 'duration': 1.371}, {'text': 'to four hours...', 'start': 216.88, 'duration': 1.519}, {'text': "you'll find that the caramel has set...", 'start': 218.399, 'duration': 2.18}, {'text': 'and we can cut it.', 'start': 220.579, 'duration': 1.45}, {'text': 'We like to cut into one-inch squares...', 'start': 222.029, 'duration': 3.12}, {'text': "but it's up to you.", 'start': 225.149, 'duration': 4.02}, {'text': 'Next for the chocolate, you need one pound of chocolate.', 'start': 229.169, 'duration': 3.08}, {'text': 'You can use milk, dark...', 'start': 232.249, 'duration': 1.88}, {'text': 'or even white chocolate for this...', 'start': 234.129, 'duration': 1.93}, {'text': 'We like to use semi-sweet.', 'start': 236.059, 'duration': 2.15}, {'text': 'Give it a chop and add to a microwave safe bowl...', 'start': 238.209, 'duration': 3.25}, {'text': 'along with two tablespoons of butter...', 'start': 241.459, 'duration': 3.14}, {'text': 'but reserve about a third cup...', 'start': 244.599, 'duration': 1.59}, {'text': ' of the chocolate...', 'start': 246.189, 'duration': 1.3}, {'text': 'to add later.
